---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Find and Compare Flight Schools (Template Preview) | Flight School Friend"
  description="This page will help future pilots compare schools by training structure, pricing, aircraft availability, scheduling, instructor fit, and goal fit."
>
  <section class="bg-white max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-20">
    <span class="inline-block px-3 py-1 bg-slate-100 text-slate-700 text-xs font-bold rounded-full mb-4 uppercase tracking-widest border border-slate-200">Template Preview</span>
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-slate-900 mb-6">Find and Compare Flight Schools</h1>
    <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 mb-10 leading-relaxed">This page will help future pilots compare schools by training structure, pricing, aircraft availability, scheduling, instructor fit, and goal fit.</p>

    <div class="space-y-8">
      <div class="bg-slate-50 p-6 rounded-2xl border border-slate-200">
        <h3 class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">What this page will eventually help compare:</h3>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-5 text-slate-600 space-y-1">
          <li>Part 61, Part 141, academy, club, and independent instructor options</li>
          <li>Aircraft rates and instructor rates</li>
          <li>Aircraft availability & Scheduling flexibility</li>
          <li>Maintenance and safety culture</li>
          <li>Instructor continuity & Student outcomes</li>
          <li>Location, commute time, and Cost transparency</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div class="border border-slate-200 p-6 rounded-2xl">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">What to verify:</h3>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-5 text-sm text-slate-500 space-y-1">
            <li>Current pricing</li>
            <li>Aircraft and instructor availability</li>
            <li>Deposit or package requirements</li>
            <li>Written refund/cancellation policies</li>
            <li>Whether the school fits your goal</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="border border-slate-200 p-6 rounded-2xl bg-amber-50 border-amber-100">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">Questions to ask:</h3>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-5 text-sm text-amber-900 space-y-1 font-medium">
            <li>How often can students realistically schedule aircraft?</li>
            <li>What does a typical student spend before checkride?</li>
            <li>Will I work with one CFI or multiple?</li>
            <li>What happens if my instructor leaves?</li>
            <li>How do you handle maintenance cancellations?</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-12 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
      <a href="/find/" class="px-6 py-3 bg-slate-100 hover:bg-slate-200 text-slate-700 font-bold rounded-lg transition text-center">&larr; Back to Find</a>
      <a href="/flight-school-decision-tool/quiz/" class="px-6 py-3 bg-sky-600 hover:bg-sky-500 text-white font-bold rounded-lg transition text-center">Start Here</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
